<view class="app-shell">
  <view class="section-card hero-card">
    <text class="hero-kicker">FARMER NOTE</text>
    <text class="hero-title">今天田里看到啥，先记下来。</text>
    <text class="hero-body">记录会自动串成时间线。带提醒的记录会同步变成一条待办，方便后面继续跟。</text>

    <view class="stats-row">
      <view class="stat-card">
        <text class="stat-value">{{stats.entryCount}}</text>
        <text class="stat-label">总记录</text>
      </view>
      <view class="stat-card">
        <text class="stat-value">{{stats.pendingTaskCount}}</text>
        <text class="stat-label">待办中</text>
      </view>
      <view class="stat-card">
        <text class="stat-value">{{stats.overdueTaskCount}}</text>
        <text class="stat-label">已逾期</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-card">
    <view class="section-heading">
      <view class="section-heading-main">
        <text class="section-title">本次记录</text>
        <text class="section-subtitle">不登录，不上云，直接保存在当前微信里。</text>
      </view>
      <text class="status-chip status-chip--success">本机保存</text>
    </view>

    <textarea
      class="textarea"
      placeholder="例如：东南角麦苗偏黄，沟边有积水，下午三点再去补看。"
      value="{{noteText}}"
      bindinput="handleNoteInput"
      auto-height
      maxlength="-1"
    />

    <text class="helper-text">支持只记文字。后面如果要继续接地块标签、病虫害分类或图片记录，这个结构也能接着扩。</text>

    <view class="toggle-row">
      <view class="toggle-main">
        <text class="toggle-label">需要定时处理吗？</text>
        <text class="toggle-caption">打开后会给这条记录挂一个时间，自动进入待办。</text>
      </view>
      <switch checked="{{reminderEnabled}}" color="#4caf50" bindchange="handleReminderToggle" />
    </view>

    <view wx:if="{{reminderEnabled}}" class="picker-grid">
      <view class="picker-field">
        <text class="picker-label">日期</text>
        <picker mode="date" value="{{reminderDate}}" bindchange="handleDateChange">
          <view class="picker-value">{{reminderDate}}</view>
        </picker>
      </view>

      <view class="picker-field">
        <text class="picker-label">时间</text>
        <picker mode="time" value="{{reminderTime}}" bindchange="handleTimeChange">
          <view class="picker-value">{{reminderTime}}</view>
        </picker>
      </view>

      <text class="helper-text">保存后会自动尝试把这条任务写入手机系统日历。如果当前微信环境或权限不支持，记录本身仍会正常保存。</text>
    </view>

    <view class="action-row action-row--single">
      <button class="action-button primary-button" bindtap="handleSave">保存这条记录</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{previewTimeText}}" class="section-card muted-card">
    <text class="preview-label">这条提醒会出现在待办里</text>
    <text class="preview-time">{{previewTimeText}}</text>
    <text class="helper-text">{{previewHint}}</text>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{feedbackMessage}}" class="section-card success-card">
    <text class="section-title">刚刚保存成功</text>
    <text class="helper-text">{{feedbackMessage}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="section-card info-card">
    <text class="section-title">下一步</text>
    <text class="helper-text">时间线会展示所有历史记录，待办页则会把挂了时间的记录自动分成即将到来、已逾期和已完成。</text>

    <view class="action-row action-row--pair">
      <button class="action-button secondary-button small-button" bindtap="goTimeline">查看时间线</button>
      <button class="action-button ghost-button small-button" bindtap="goTasks">打开待办</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="nav-bar">
    <button class="nav-item nav-item--active" bindtap="goRecord">记录</button>
    <button class="nav-item" bindtap="goTimeline">时间线</button>
    <button class="nav-item" bindtap="goTasks">待办</button>
  </view>
</view>
